room_title: Escape room "20,000 Leaks Under The Sea" by House of Conundrum in Omaha
review: Our family of six absolutely loved the House of Conundrum! We booked a time for 20,000 Leaks Under the Sea. It was intense, exciting and so mind-provoking! Even our 9 and 11-year-old children were easily engaged. If you're looking for a fun family bonding activity, this is the place! The staff were incredibly kind and encouraging! Can't wait to go again!

room_title: Escape room "20,000 Leaks Under The Sea" by House of Conundrum in Omaha
review: What a fun and creative experience!! We did 20,000 Leaks Under the Sea. Our first time doing anything like this and it was a great time!
